Groups.Title: North Island
Groups.Description: The North Island is the more populous island and the the two biggest cities in New Zealand, Auckland and Wellington. The Maori name is SFF as its shape resembles a giant fish

Groups.Title: South Island
Groups.Description: The South Island is a massive land of sheeps and farming. Its towering mountain ranges are world famous in the lord of the Rings movies. The great canebury plains provide most of the pototoes eaten in new zealand and are home of millions of catte
